In 2020, the racial and ethnic makeup was 85.21% [[Non-Hispanic whites|non-Hispanic White]], 0.83% Black, 0.02% Native American or Alaska Native, 4.57% Asian, 0.2% some other race or ethnicity, 3.91% multiracial, and 5.25% Hispanic or Latino residents of any race.<ref name=":0" />

According to the [[2010 United States census|2010 U.S. census]],<ref name="GR2" /> there were 8,564 people, 3,411 households, and 2,426 families residing in the town. At the [[2020 United States census]], there were 8,864 people, 3,398 households, and 2,562 families residing in the town.<ref name=":0" />

Among the population in 2010, the racial makeup was 94.4% [[White (U.S. Census)|White]], 0.5% [[African American (U.S. Census)|African American]], 0.0% [[Native American (U.S. Census)|Native American]], 2.8% [[Asian (U.S. Census)|Asian]], 0.0% [[Pacific Islander (U.S. Census)|Pacific Islander]], 1.0% from [[Race (United States Census)|other races]], and 1.1% from two or more races. In addition, [[Hispanic (U.S. Census)|Hispanic]] or [[Latino (U.S. Census)|Latino]] residents of any race were 4.0% of the population.<ref name = "US Census">{{cite web | url = http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/SAFFFacts?_event=&geo_id=16000US4833824&_geoContext=01000US%7c04000US48%7c16000US4833824&_street=&_county=Highland+Park%2C+tx&_cityTown=Highland+Park%2C+tx&_state=&_zip=&_lang=en&_sse=on&ActiveGeoDiv=&_useEV=&pctxt=fph&pgsl=160&_submenuId=factsheet_1&ds_name=null&_ci_nbr=null&qr_name=null&reg=null%3Anull&_keyword=&_industry=&show_2003_tab=&redirect=Y | archive-url = https://archive.today/20200210222312/http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/SAFFFacts?_event=&geo_id=16000US4833824&_geoContext=01000US%7C04000US48%7C16000US4833824&_street=&_county=Highland+Park,+tx&_cityTown=Highland+Park,+tx&_state=&_zip=&_lang=en&_sse=on&ActiveGeoDiv=&_useEV=&pctxt=fph&pgsl=160&_submenuId=factsheet_1&ds_name=null&_ci_nbr=null&qr_name=null&reg=null:null&_keyword=&_industry=&show_2003_tab=&redirect=Y | url-status = dead | archive-date = February 10, 2020 | title = Highland Park town, Texas | publisher = US Census | access-date = January 9, 2010 }}</ref>

